'''Senior Trooper''' was an enlisted rank below that of a [[Sergeant/Legends|sergeant]] in several [[Army/Legends|armies]], such as the [[Alliance Special Forces/Legends|Alliance Special Forces]]<ref name="ROE">''[[Rules of Engagement: The Rebel SpecForce Handbook]]''</ref> and the [[Brotherhood of Darkness/Legends|Brotherhood of Darkness]]. [[Adanar]] was an example of a Senior Trooper.<ref name="DB">''[[Darth Bane: Path of Destruction]]''</ref>

